Description: Episcope provides a reproducible framework for constructing and comparing gene regulatory networks by integrating bulk ATAC-seq footprinting with matched RNA-seq expression data. It implements context-specific enhancerâ€“gene linking, TF-centric and differential GRN analysis, and benchmarking modules. Episcope enables systematic exploration of transcriptional regulation under diverse conditions.
